    "description": "Whether data is in-flight or at rest, whether it is whole and in one place or fragmented and distributed across the infrastructure, the Leonovus Cryptographic Module ensures the critical data elements are secured with state-of-the-art encryption and decryption algorithms. Because of the Leonovus Cryptographic Module, the IT organization retains control over the keys independent of the storage infrastructure and services. In this manner, IT regains its control over the data while greatly improving the flexibility on where it flows and resides.",
